{
  "text": "The prokaryotic expression and purification of Histagged OCT4A (His-OCT4A) recombinant proteins was conducted as previously described [CITATION_1] . The enhanced WBbased quantification of endogenous OCT4A protein was carried out as described in the Supplementary Materials and Methods.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "25827367"
